Package author: Igor Gaponenko

Brief description:
==================

This is the Registry Database for LCLS ONLINE and OFLINE systems. The database
stores information about instruments, experimental groups, experiments, etc.

Detailed description:
=====================

The package contains:

- database schema
- PHP library for accessing and manipulating the database contents
- Pythin library and tools to access and manipulate the database contents
- a reference Web application for the database
